OL,3,C'It needs to go further': mum's
OL,4,Cdisappointment with road safety
OL,5,Cstrategy
OL,7,FAs well as new alcohol limits and eye
OL,8,Ftests for older drivers, the
OL,9,FGovernment's proposals for a new road
OL,10,Fsafety strategy does include a minimum
OL,11,Flearning period for new drivers, which
OL,12,Fcould allow them to develop skills
OL,13,Fwhen driving on a variety of roads and
OL,14,Fin different weather conditions.
OL,16,FHowever, the plans don't include any
OL,17,Frestrictions on drivers after they
OL,18,Fpass their test - something Sharron
OL,19,Fsays she is disappointed with.
