OL,3,C'It needs to go further': mum's
OL,4,Cdisappointment with road safety
OL,5,Cstrategy
OL,7,FShe said: "I'm pleased that we now
OL,8,Fhave a road safety strategy, because
OL,9,Fwe've waited 14 years for one, but I
OL,10,Fdon't think that the element of young
OL,11,Fdrivers goes far enough. What we need
OL,12,Fis also the post-test safety
OL,13,Fprecautions for our young drivers,
OL,14,Fbecause that's when the crashes are
OL,15,Foccurring.
