OL,3,C'It needs to go further': mum's
OL,4,Cdisappointment with road safety
OL,5,Cstrategy
OL,7,FSharron advocates for the use of
OL,8,FGraduated Driving Licences, which
OL,9,Fcould see rules that restrict the
OL,10,Fhours in which young drivers can
OL,11,Ftravel and prevent them from carrying
OL,12,Fpassengers of the same age, in the
OL,13,Ffirst six months after they pass their
OL,14,Ftest.
