OL,3,C'It needs to go further': mum's
OL,4,Cdisappointment with road safety
OL,5,Cstrategy
OL,7,FShe told ITV News: "(After Caitlin's
OL,8,Fdeath) I found out about graduated
OL,9,Fdriving licences. The one element that
OL,10,Fstood out to me was that newly
OL,11,Fqualified young drivers don't carry
OL,12,Ftheir peer-aged friends as passengers
OL,13,Ffor a limited time.
OL,15,F"A graduated driving licence is law in
OL,16,Fother countries. It is a phased
OL,17,Flicensing system, it supports young
OL,18,Fdrivers through their early stages
OL,19,Fwhen they're inexperienced."
