OL,3,C'It needs to go further': mum's
OL,4,Cdisappointment with road safety
OL,5,Cstrategy
OL,7,F"Before they drive, (young drivers)
OL,8,Fdon't go anywhere in a car, so all
OL,9,Fwe're asking for is this limited
OL,10,Fperiod of six months after learning to
OL,11,Fdrive to not carry peer-age
OL,12,Fpassengers. It doesn't stop you from
OL,13,Ftravelling with an older, experienced
OL,14,Fdriver, and if you are a teenage
OL,15,Fparent who does want to put your
OL,16,Fchildren in the car, there are
OL,17,Fexemptions.
OL,26,@oD@UpmoD@cpn
