OL,3,C'It needs to go further': mum's
OL,4,Cdisappointment with road safety
OL,5,Cstrategy
OL,7,F"It works for other countries so why
OL,8,Fcan't it work in the UK? If there's
OL,9,Fanyone who needs to get to work, there
OL,10,Fare exemptions for that too."
OL,12,FSharron credits the publication of a
OL,13,F'Report to Prevent Future Deaths'
OL,14,Fafter the inquest into Caitlin's death
OL,15,Ffor giving her the courage to start
OL,16,Fher road safety campaign.
OL,18,FShe said: "That gave me the courage to
OL,19,Fset up this campaign in Caitlin's
OL,20,Fname, and gave me the courage to speak
OL,21,Fup.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/11
