OL,3,C'It needs to go further': mum's
OL,4,Cdisappointment with road safety
OL,5,Cstrategy
OL,7,F"We've now got another six families
OL,8,Fthat have got a preventing future
OL,9,Fdeaths report, all calling for a
OL,10,Fgraduated driving licence. I don't
OL,11,Fthink the Government should ignore
OL,12,Fthese calls."
OL,14,FReflecting on her daughter's life,
OL,15,FSharron believes her daughter would
OL,16,Fapprove of her campaigning.
OL,18,FShe said: "I know that she would want
OL,19,Fme to do this. I think Caitlin would
OL,20,Fdefinitely be going to me, 'come on
OL,21,Fmam, get this law implemented'.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/11
