OL,3,C'It needs to go further': mum's
OL,4,Cdisappointment with road safety
OL,5,Cstrategy
OL,7,FThe Government says its Road Safety
OL,8,FStrategy, which is the first of its
OL,9,Fkind in over a decade, aims to reduce
OL,10,Froad deaths and serious injuries by
OL,11,F65% by 2035.
OL,13,FIt added that it will save thousands
OL,14,Fof lives - whilst also reducing
OL,15,Fpressure on the NHS and making
OL,16,Fcommunities safer - by tackling drink
OL,17,Fdriving, improving training for young
OL,18,Fdrivers, and introducing mandatory eye
OL,19,Ftests for older motorists.
